platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: While Hitman GO carved out a bold new direction for Agent 47, his next iOS mission expertly captures the riveting gameplay of the venerable console series. You wont be donning disguises to sneak into enemy compounds (the games all about sniping), but you still carefully scout each location, unravel the intricately woven level design, and then strike with impeccable timingor die and try again. Hitman: Sniper does its legacy proud with 150 missions full of engrossing action and the series quirky sense of humor.
